Bullet

public Bullet(int initX,
              int initY,
              int targetX,
              int targetY,
              int initR,
              int type,
              int life)
Initialize a new bullet with the specified parameters.

Parameters:
initX - X coordinate of initial position.
initY - Y coordinate of initial position.
targetX - X coordinate of target position.
targetY - Y coordinate of target position.
initR - Initial bullet radius.
type - Type of bullet to create.
life - lifespan of bullet in frames.
